css- cascade stylesheet

use of css style 
    1. inner style in any tag
    2. in the same html documet in head tag
    3. on other file linked using ref

css selector

    1. Element selector
    2. id selector 
    3. class selector

        selector preference when used in same tag
        //it use the  id>class>element 

