css color 
can be use many 
    1. RGB
    2. Rgba (rgb alpha) //alpha ka vale 0-1 use to show transparency 
    3. HEX //hexadecimal
    4. HSl //hue(0-360 degree),saturation(0-100%), lightness(0-100%)
    5. HSla (alpha) it also uses transparency
    
css background

can be used color and image 
    for image 
        /* image can also be use 
        background-image: url('image source')*/

    for color 
        /* background-color: */
        is used

